Viva - Global Medical Records System
A global medical records system backed by blockchain technology, with a builtin international
payment network. With the ability to perform deep learning queries across the entire dataset and
that can be used to train the next generation of AI systems to spot signs of chronic disease long
before they have a chance to become life threatening issues.
If we can get development funding, we're planning on entering this system and
it's distributed AI architecture in the IBM sponsored XPrize for AI --> www.xprize.org/ai
Essentially our goal is to build the worlds largest and fastest AI system using peer to peer technologies and
make it purpose built for the healthcare sector.
At the same time, the secure medical records storage aspect would be a gold mine to researchers.

"It is not just an App... we are setting a standard" - Devin Luker
A method of electronically recording, submitting, securing, tabulating and verifying voting results in real time,
and providing for real-time 3rd-party oversight and documentation of the same.
